    <div class="py-2">
        <text class="text-lg">
          My research focuses on <b>system Human-Computer Interaction (HCI)</b> and <b>Cognitive Science</b>.
          Recently, I focus on <b>intent-level</b> human-computer interaction. 
          More specifically, I hope to leverage interfaces to improve communication between two black boxes- humans and AI. 
          <br/>
          <br/>
          I address this issue in three directions: 
        </text>
        <ul>
